                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi>
                  </rs>. <hi rend="largeCaps">SAM BROOK</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">was further charged with a previous conviction of felony at Newington, in March</hi>, 1873, <hi rend="italic">to which he</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>**—<hi rend="italic">
